<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.10">
<l>meynniṉṟa pāva makala tirumālaik</l>
<l>kainniṉṟa vāḻiyāṉ cūḻuṅ kaḻalcūṭi</l>
<l>kainniṉṟa vēṟkaik kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>yaiyoṉṟu maintu mivaipāṭi yāṭumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that the sins that abide in your body depart, dance, singing of Tirumāl,</l>
<l>[With] these five-and-five [verses] of the garland of words of Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l>Who hurls a spear which abides in his hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">having crowned [himself] with the anklets</l>
<l>Encircling [the feet] of the one with a discus that abides in his hand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
